contact_tracing:
Immediately if you have come in contact with someone outside the workplace
that tests positive.
• Notify your supervisor that you have come in contact with someone who tested positive for
Covid-19.
• Be aware you may be contacted by a contact tracer from the health department.
self_reporting: If you are suffering from COVID-19 symptoms (those symptoms are fever; cough; shortness of breath; aching; loss of taste; loss of smell; sore throat) please leave the campus for testing.
